<br />\n做唔到同唔做唔識分啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估我地香港人好似你地咁低賤要靠黃賭毒先生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bbe55e72a29c83d5e211fffd81da552a551320","tid":296673,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:42:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁叻仲上連登<br />\n返澳門討論區打飛機啦 其實有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果香港搞賭場 唔駛兩年收哂你成個澳門皮<br />\n你信唔信<br />\n<br />\n掉番轉你澳門有冇可能變金融中心<br />\n有咩真係一等既Ibank 同private bank 係澳門<br />\n<br />\n只有窮人先會以為澳門好<br />\n<br />\n講top level根本蚊同牛比</blockquote><br />\n香港係國際金融中心，係國際貿易中心，咁又點？<br />\n對你有無咩正負面影響？<br />\n係咪可以大聲d同人講我住喺個國際城市入面，好撚巴鳩閉？<br />\n澳門平均人工高香港少少，工時一定短過香港，樓價低好多，物價就差唔到<br />\n你係要比較ge，都搵d貼身少少ge去比較啦柒頭<br />\n<br />\n利申返先：我係香港人"},{"pid":"eec3bb063b4884a4f1cd19116d38e126af6393b1","tid":296673,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:44:57.000Z","msg":"事實上的確係有班澳門人好憎香港人<br />\n而亦都有班港豬盲反澳狗<br />\n<br />\n就好似極端黃絲藍絲咁，討厭黎都嘥鳩氣"},{"pid":"11f03ea41fb21d25d25fac4580cf436462b822d6","tid":296673,"uid":85762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上面d巴打傻左？有咩好拗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">澳門好正做澳門人最幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港好大壓力環境好差又冇福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人個個都想做澳門人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快d share去大陸forum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黎澳門生仔係無身分證的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f704e315d1fbd5bb0cf25005df11a34672c4aee","tid":296673,"uid":127569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"成班澳門狗係到打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係到幻想澳門好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚好你地就唔駛成日痴香港著數啦。睇醫生，買野，搭飛機甚至乎連個討論區都要痴過來r水吹，仲要睇唔起香港人。果然澳門狗同支那狗一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbdd83660447208eddca06bee4abaf61bf75d8d","tid":296673,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上面d巴打傻左？有咩好拗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">澳門好正做澳門人最幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港好大壓力環境好差又冇福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人個個都想做澳門人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快d share去大陸forum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黎澳門生仔係無身分證的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個話要去生仔<br />\n依家d人黎香港都唔係靠生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地自有佢地ge辦法"},{"pid":"0f09aaf278955bd87267c1e4c8c9dd2eadc410ff","tid":296673,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />擺上天涯分享下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7dc1900eeaeea479fad2bb6c2160c6f271330ab","tid":296673,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班澳門狗係到打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係到幻想澳門好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl